@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
title Supply Inventory State Transition

[*] --> InStock : Supply added

InStock --> Sufficient : Above reorder point
InStock --> LowStock : At/below reorder point
InStock --> OutOfStock : Quantity = 0

Sufficient --> LowStock : Stock depleted
LowStock --> Sufficient : Stock replenished
LowStock --> OutOfStock : Fully consumed

OutOfStock --> OrderPlaced : Purchase order created
LowStock --> OrderPlaced : Reorder triggered

OrderPlaced --> InTransit : Order confirmed
InTransit --> Receiving : Delivery arrived
Receiving --> InStock : Stock updated

InStock --> Reserved : Pullout approved
Reserved --> InStock : Pullout returned/cancelled
Reserved --> Consumed : Supplies used

Consumed --> InStock : Stock level updated

InStock --> Expired : Past expiration date
Expired --> Disposed : Removed from inventory

Disposed --> [*] : Item discarded

Sufficient : Stock healthy
Sufficient : No action needed

LowStock : Alert generated
LowStock : Reorder recommended

OutOfStock : Cannot fulfill pullouts
OutOfStock : Purchase required

Reserved : Allocated to service
Reserved : Temporarily unavailable

@enduml
